        "cooked": "<p>Peace</p>\n<p>I’m trying to figure out how to make the voice note preview show before sending the voice note. I don’t want it to automatically send when I release my finger - I want to listen to it first.</p>\n<p>I’ve seen the preview show up from time to time, but I can’t seem to trigger it willingly or know what I did for the preview to show up with the play button?</p>\n<p>Thanks</p>",
