        "cooked": "<p>Hi there,</p>\n<p>If you make a voice message you can click anywhere on the screen after to pause it and then you can listen to it before you send.</p>\n<p>You cannot continue with the current message after, only <strong>delete</strong> it or <strong>send</strong> it.</p>",
